就玩埋啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa631c1bbb9ba88bd89d668b8d3359758caaa6c","tid":271971,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Galgame剩係係中學果陣接觸過key社果幾隻<br />\nAir Kanon clannad 仲有隻智代after story<br />\n次次玩完都好灰<br />\n自此對galgame有好負面既印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推薦多隻你玩 <br />\n素晴日 一定唔可以睇劇透"},{"pid":"d5d19b9cc9d9fd16756cb306f8a783661b73a904","tid":271971,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T22:18:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2f3e48b61462e4d733761d0f09b5273219e1e7e","tid":271971,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GALGAME其實好好玩, 但要搵岩自己口味既黎玩, 因為真係太多選擇<br />\n<br />\n你唔好沉重悲情既走去玩初雪櫻就實會喊到仆街<br />\n你鍾意日常攪笑既玩天神亂漫就會覺得好正</blockquote><br />\n以前我鐘意玩逆轉裁判呀機戰果d<br />\n後黎人懶唔想操作就揀剩係睇劇情既gal😩<br />\n不過persona5又玩番<br />\n但係操作都係有啲嫌煩😂"},{"pid":"d89d6b68523b2a4ceeda0867941946bd667c23c9","tid":271971,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Galgame剩係係中學果陣接觸過key社果幾隻<br />\nAir Kanon clannad 仲有隻智代after story<br />\n次次玩完都好灰<br />\n自此對galgame有好負面既印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推薦多隻你玩 <br />\n素晴日 一定唔可以睇劇透</blockquote><br />\n啱啱玩完素晴日，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c315c45a57ae3d0b9f222934b07f2f79df99c9af","tid":271971,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Galgame剩係係中學果陣接觸過key社果幾隻<br />\nAir Kanon clannad 仲有隻智代after story<br />\n次次玩完都好灰<br />\n自此對galgame有好負面既印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"